tip.text: If you need to use a credit card just look for the credit card company logo on the back window of the taxi. If it is there just sit in -  do not ask if they take card because they do not like cards.
Ask for the swordfish collar, they will tell you it takes 30 minutes but just ask for it. The huge portion of fish is worth every chunk of the protein packed goodness it comes with. Best dish here.
